Class NondominatedSetConstructor

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.polytechtours.prd.multiagent.heuristic.meta.NondominatedSetConstructor

  • public class NondominatedSetConstructor
extends java.lang.Object
    This class provides methods to sort the population by their level of dominant
    In return, several sets are returned in order of their rank of dominant
    The lower rank comes first
